<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Schwabach</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung für Berthold Holbier, Bürger zu Nürnberg, der sich wegen eines Streits mit einem Schwabacher Bürger auf dem dortigen Markt morgen rechtfertigen muss.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_139" id="69r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_139_r2l12">Swobach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_139_r2l13">Lieben frewnd / vns hat fürgelegt Bertholt Holbier <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / wie er auf ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l14"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> tag Sünvvenden <expan>nehſtvergange<ex>n</ex></expan> beÿ ew auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Margkt geweſen ſeÿ / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l15">daʒ ſich etvvas vnvvillen vnd <expan>miſſhandlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> mit <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒwiſchen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l16">vnd Jm <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / darv̈mb er ſich auf <expan>morge<ex>n</ex></expan> vor ew <expan>ſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> müſʒ / <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l17">daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / darÿnne <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> güten willen <expan>ercʒeige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l18">vnd Jm der ſach gütlichen cʒerÿnnen <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria ut <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_139" id="69r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Swobach</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnd, uns hat fürgelegt Bertholt Holbier,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie er <app><note><q type="date">auf sant
                            <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> tag sünwenden
                            <expan>nehstvergange<ex>n</ex></expan></q>24.06.1410</note></app> bey ew auf
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> margkt gewesen sey und daz sich etwas
                        unwillen und <expan>misshandlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> mit
                            <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> czwischen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> und im <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, darümb er sich <app><note><q type="date">auf
                            <expan>morge<ex>n</ex></expan></q>31.06.1410</note></app> vor ew <expan>stelle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        müsz. <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynne <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> güten
                        willen <expan>erczeige<ex>n</ex></expan> und im der sach gütlichen czerynnen
                                <expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
